@verbose 0.1.0

concept P256ScalarState
  @intention: "P-256 scalar mult state: Jacobian accumulator Q + running point P (X|Y|Z, 30 limbs each) + infinity flag + bit counter j + which + 64-hex-char big-endian scalar"
